-- Bruce Ratner Discusses Nassau Coliseum Redevelopment (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-08-06T12:11:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-06/bruce-ratner-discusses-nassau-coliseum-redevelopment-audio-.html
Bruce Ratner, chairman and founder of
Forest City Ratner Cos., says the affluence of New York State's 
Nassau County means a "terrific demographic" will purchase 
tickets to the renovated Nassau Coliseum. Ratner talks with 
Bloomberg's  Tom Keene  and Scarlet Fu on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."      (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 09:32
 